ndsong</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/3/02 5:37:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Unanimous opinion which armor is the best...</span><hr size=1> In general, for all classes:<br><br>SS has the best stats.<br>Kael has the best AC.<br>Thurgadin is easy to get. <p><b><a target="_blank" href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6856>Dastin Windsong</a></b><br>Bard of the 60th Song<br><b><a target="_blank" href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8556>Dagnil</a></b><br>Monk of 45 bloody knuckles<br><i><a target="_blank" href=http://www.methodsofmadness.org>Methods of Madness</a></i><br><img src=http://publish.hometown.aol.com/dastinwindsong/images/bardpreferred.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umagatone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Magatone</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/3/02 9:08:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://userpages.umbc.edu/~eberry1/images/bm3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Unanimous opinion which armor is the best...</span><hr size=1> There's a wonderful chart detailing all of these stats here on Graffe's in the Library. Just for convenience, you can find it all <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.graffe.com/library/velious_armor_comparison.htm">here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br><br>If you just want an opinion though, I'd 